00:10:58.830 --> 00:10:59.710
this deep sense of

00:10:59.799 --> 00:11:01.269
understanding we want is.

00:11:01.580 --> 00:11:03.429
It is a fact that everyone changes,

00:11:03.820 --> 00:11:04.929
often in huge and

00:11:04.929 --> 00:11:06.009
unpredictable ways.

00:11:06.480 --> 00:11:07.169
If we're looking to

00:11:07.169 --> 00:11:08.350
be understood in a

00:11:08.350 --> 00:11:10.139
deep, almost intuitive way,

00:11:10.799 --> 00:11:11.350
how can that be

00:11:11.350 --> 00:11:12.309
reconciled with the

00:11:12.360 --> 00:11:13.470
dynamic nature of identity?

00:11:13.830 --> 00:11:15.009
There are clearly

00:11:15.009 --> 00:11:15.990
some types of love

00:11:15.990 --> 00:11:16.929
that can and

00:11:17.000 --> 00:11:18.049
perhaps should persist

00:11:18.049 --> 00:11:19.370
in spite of understanding.

00:11:19.620 --> 00:11:20.830
Parental love might require

00:11:20.830 --> 00:11:21.789
