00:11:21.789 --> 00:11:22.950
child even if

00:11:22.950 --> 00:11:23.769
they don't understand

00:11:23.769 --> 00:11:24.649
their life choices.

00:11:25.100 --> 00:11:26.269
Being a good political

00:11:26.460 --> 00:11:27.710
subject might require us

00:11:27.710 --> 00:11:28.590
to care about our

00:11:28.779 --> 00:11:30.049
