00:11:30.049 --> 00:11:30.970
even if we

00:11:30.970 --> 00:11:32.059
don't understand each other.

00:11:32.340 --> 00:11:33.509
True religious love looks

00:11:33.559 --> 00:11:34.549
like loving thy neighbor

00:11:34.549 --> 00:11:35.929
even when they ascribe

00:11:35.929 --> 00:11:36.860
to a different religion.

00:11:37.279 --> 00:11:37.809
But why does

00:11:37.809 --> 00:11:39.370
understanding feel so crucial

00:11:39.370 --> 00:11:40.909
to romantic relationships?

00:11:41.330 --> 00:11:41.830
This might have

00:11:41.830 --> 00:11:42.230
to do with

00:11:42.230 --> 00:11:43.029
the fact that when

00:11:43.029 --> 00:11:43.590
we love someone,

00:11:44.309 --> 00:11:44.870
we love the

00:11:44.870 --> 00:11:46.080
particular individual,

00:11:46.580 --> 00:11:47.409
not just the combination

00:11:47.409 --> 00:11:48.870
of qualities they have.

00:11:49.139 --> 00:11:50.110
Most philosophers of

00:11:50.120 --> 00:11:50.990
love reject the

00:11:51.159 --> 00:11:51.929
quality view of

00:11:52.000 --> 00:11:52.870
love because if

00:11:52.870 --> 00:11:53.850
we loved people based

00:11:53.850 --> 00:11:54.809
on their qualities,

00:11:55.210 --> 00:11:55.570
then we could

00:11:55.570 --> 00:11:57.009
