00:11:57.009 --> 00:11:57.809
that churned out

00:11:57.809 --> 00:11:58.570
perfect lovers.

00:11:58.929 --> 00:11:59.289
Or when you

00:11:59.289 --> 00:12:00.110
lost a loved one,

00:12:00.210 --> 00:12:01.289
you could simply replace

00:12:01.399 --> 00:12:02.110
them with someone

00:12:02.110 --> 00:12:02.720
with the same qualities.

00:12:03.419 --> 00:12:04.450
To understand someone

00:12:04.450 --> 00:12:05.169
shows that you

00:12:05.169 --> 00:12:06.429
get me as a

00:12:06.429 --> 00:12:07.259
particular individual.

00:12:07.960 --> 00:12:08.370
But this is

00:12:08.370 --> 00:12:09.269
where the tension between

00:12:09.299 --> 00:12:10.269
understanding and

00:12:10.269 --> 00:12:11.340
love becomes evident.

00:12:11.629 --> 00:12:12.950
The unique particularity

00:12:12.950 --> 00:12:14.529
of each individual is

00:12:14.529 --> 00:12:15.710
precisely what gets in

00:12:15.710 --> 00:12:16.850
the way of understanding.

00:12:20.799 --> 00:12:21.720
The individual is

00:12:21.720 --> 00:12:22.440
both a subject

00:12:22.440 --> 00:12:23.159
with the ability

00:12:23.159 --> 00:12:24.279
to change and

00:12:24.279 --> 00:12:25.480
an object constrained

00:12:25.480 --> 00:12:26.440
by static facts.

