about the self,

00:12:57.399 --> 00:12:58.159
we change how we

00:12:58.159 --> 00:12:59.460
understand and carry ourselves.

00:13:00.000 --> 00:13:00.840
But this process of

00:13:00.840 --> 00:13:02.720
reinterpretation doesn't happen alone.

00:13:03.000 --> 00:13:03.899
Much of our identity

00:13:03.899 --> 00:13:05.259
and self-conception comes

00:13:05.259 --> 00:13:06.620
from seeing ourselves through

00:13:06.620 --> 00:13:07.639
the eyes of others.

00:13:08.019 --> 00:13:08.919
Love's gaze sees

00:13:08.919 --> 00:13:10.740
us in a particularly intimate way.

00:13:11.019 --> 00:13:11.820
It peeks through the

00:13:11.820 --> 00:13:12.779
barriers we usually

00:13:12.779 --> 00:13:13.639
put up for others.

00:13:14.076 --> 00:13:15.440
"The other's look

00:13:15.440 --> 00:13:16.460
fashions my body

00:13:16.539 --> 00:13:17.080
in its nakedness,

00:13:17.759 --> 00:13:18.120
causes it

00:13:18.120 --> 00:13:18.740
to be born,

00:13:19.179 --> 00:13:20.240
sculptors it, produces

00:13:20.240 --> 00:13:21.039
it as it is,

00:13:21.840 --> 00:13:22.580
sees it as I

00:13:22.580 --> 00:13:23.519
shall never see it.

00:13:23.700 --> 00:13:24.039
The other

00:13:24.039 --> 00:13:24.779
holds a secret,

00:13:25.200 --> 00:13:25.919
the secret of

00:13:25.919 --> 00:13:26.580
what I am."

00:13:27.080 --> 00:13:28.200
Thus, love tends to

00:13:28.200 --> 00:13:29.899
change us often unexpectedly.

00:13:30.379 --> 00:13:31.519
We may find behavior,

00:13:31.779 --> 00:13:32.840
habits, interests, and

00:13:32.840 --> 00:13:34.039
beliefs altered through

00:13:34.039 --> 00:13:34.740
a loving relationship.

00:13:35.519 --> 00:13:36.480
Different facts about our

00:13:36.480 --> 00:13:37.679
lives become salient to

00:13:37.679 --> 00:13:38.440
us depending on

00:13:38.440 --> 00:13:39.240
the self-conception

00:13:39.379 --> 00:13:40.039
we ascribe to.

00:13:40.500 --> 00:13:41.080
And our behavior

00:13:41.080 --> 00:13:42.139
will change to reflect

00:13:42.139 --> 00:13:43.220
new self-conceptions.

00:13:43.659 --> 00:13:44.419
But this entails

00:13:44.419 --> 00:13:45.460
that being understood

00:13:45.480 --> 00:13:46.379
is never guaranteed.

00:13:47.120 --> 00:13:47.500
Someone could

00:13:47.500 --> 00:13:48.480
understand you very

00:13:48.480 --> 00:13:49.279
well in the first

00:13:49.279 --> 00:13:50.200
few years of dating,

00:13:50.600 --> 00:13:50.960
but through

00:13:50.960 --> 00:13:51.759
loving each other,

00:13:52.159 --> 00:13:53.379
each person changes and

00:13:53.620 --> 00:13:54.220
actually comes to

00:13:54.240 --> 00:13:55.379
understand the other less.

00:13:55.840 --> 00:13:56.659
Sometimes lovers

00:13:56.659 --> 00:13:57.639
outgrow each other,

00:13:57.740 --> 00:13:58.700
but they also couldn't

00:13:58.740 --> 00:13:59.299
have done that

00:13:59.299 --> 00:14:00.539
growing without each other.

00:14:00.759 --> 00:14:01.500
The tension between

00:14:01.519 --> 00:14:02.879
our subjectivity and our

00:14:02.879 --> 00:14:04.700
objectivity makes it impossible

00:14:04.700 --> 00:14:05.860
to reduce people to

00:14:05.940 --> 00:14:07.220
some higher coherent

00:14:07.220 --> 00:14:08.500
principle that makes sense.

00:14:08.960 --> 00:14:10.159
Individuals are full of

00:14:10.259 --> 00:14:11.500
contradiction and rich history.

00:14:12.031 --> 00:14:13.159
"What if the other

00:14:13.159 --> 00:14:14.039
is irreducible,

00:14:14.360 --> 00:14:14.960
not only to

00:14:14.960 --> 00:14:16.000
my or our thought,

00:14:16.539 --> 00:14:17.700
but to thought as such?"

00:14:18.019 --> 00:14:18.639
Put another way,

00:14:18.980 --> 00:14:19.820
is love reducible

00:14:19.820 --> 00:14:20.440
to a feature

00:14:20.440 --> 00:14:21.039
of the intellect,

00:14:21.379 --> 00:14:21.980
like understanding?

00:14:22.460 --> 00:14:23.000
Or does love

00:14:23.000 --> 00:14:25.120
necessarily escape intellectual bounds?

00:14:25.600 --> 00:14:26.299
Sartre thought love

00:14:26.299 --> 00:14:26.860
could never be

00:14:26.860 --> 00:14:28.000
confined by understanding,

00:14:28.019 --> 00:14:28.899
which made love

00:14:28.899 --> 00:14:29.759
a failed project.

00:14:30.159 --> 00:14:31.159
Here's the dilemma. We

00:14:31.159 --> 00:14:32.379
gain a stable conception

00:14:32.399 --> 00:14:33.200
of ourselves through

00:14:33.200 --> 00:14:34.320
our lover's perception.

00:14:34.659 --> 00:14:36.159
Facing our subjectivity, our

00:14:36.159 --> 00:14:37.580
innate potential for change,

00:14:38.000 --> 00:14:39.159
that's scary. But in

00:14:39.159 --> 00:14:40.100
the eyes of love,

00:14:40.340 --> 00:14:41.899
we can escape subjectivity

00:14:42.019 --> 00:14:42.940
and feel understood

00:14:42.960 --> 00:14:44.320
as a coherent object.

00:14:44.779 --> 00:14:45.539
We think of ourselves

00:14:45.539 --> 00:14:46.879
as funny or smart

00:14:46.879 --> 00:14:48.320
or kind because our

00:14:48.320 --> 00:14:49.240
lover's treatment of

00:14:49.240 --> 00:14:50.299
us affirms that we

00:14:50.299 --> 00:14:50.879
are those things.

00:14:51.460 --> 00:14:52.559
Mundane facts like the

00:14:52.659 --> 00:14:53.480
veins on my hands,

00:14:53.820 --> 00:14:55.320
the way
one's eyelashes curl,

00:14:55.600 --> 00:14:56.379
the slight gap

00:14:56.379 --> 00:14:57.379
between one's teeth.

00:14:57.620 --> 00:14:58.299
The gaze of

00:14:58.299 --> 00:14:59.320
our lover gives these

00:14:59.500 --> 00:15:00.700
facts value and

00:15:00.700 --> 00:15:02.179
thus reasons to exist.

00:15:02.600 --> 00:15:03.379
But here's the

00:15:03.379 --> 00:15:04.259
other scary part.

00:15:04.620 --> 00:15:05.379
Our lover is a

00:15:05.379 --> 00:15:06.500
subject who can change.

00:15:06.919 --> 00:15:07.460
Who's to say

00:15:07.460 --> 00:15:08.340
they will perceive me

00:15:08.340 --> 00:15:08.919
the same way

00:15:08.919 --> 00:15:10.700
forever or even tomorrow?

00:15:10.700 --> 00:15:12.159
But if they change,

00:15:12.379 --> 00:15:12.919
then my sense

00:15:12.919 --> 00:15:14.409
of self also destabilizes.

00:15:15.120 --> 00:15:15.500
Just tell

00:15:15.500 --> 00:15:16.240
me the truth!

00:15:19.350 --> 00:15:19.990
Chase! You're

00:15:19.990 --> 00:15:21.029
scaring me, Pearl.

00:15:21.350 --> 00:15:21.970
But I also

00:15:21.970 --> 00:15:23.110
can't control them to

00:15:23.230 --> 00:15:23.830
stay the same,

00:15:24.179 --> 00:15:25.490
otherwise their perception of

00:15:25.490 --> 00:15:26.330
me is not genuine.

00:15:27.059 --> 00:15:27.559
And again,

00:15:27.830 --> 00:15:28.490
I might also

00:15:28.490 --> 00:15:29.350
change through their

00:15:29.350 --> 00:15:30.269
perception of me.

00:15:30.529 --> 00:15:31.210
If to be loved

00:15:31.210 --> 00:15:32.110
is to be understood,

00:15:32.500 --> 00:15:33.929
then will
love always fail?

00:15:34.360 --> 00:15:35.149
Call me a romantic,

00:15:35.210 --> 00:15:35.870
but I

00:15:35.870 --> 00:15:36.799
hate that conclusion.

00:15:37.580 --> 00:15:38.570
I want love to

00:15:38.570 --> 00:15:39.850
succeed, goddammit.

00:15:40.299 --> 00:15:40.789
There are two

00:15:40.789 --> 00:15:41.389
ways we might

00:15:41.389 --> 00:15:42.269
move forward then.

00:15:42.559 --> 00:15:43.330
One option is

00:15:43.330 --> 00:15:44.110
to just accept

00:15:44.269 --> 00:15:44.710
that no one

00:15:44.710 --> 00:15:45.509
can ever wholly

00:15:45.509 --> 00:15:46.509
understand each other,

00:15:46.950 --> 00:15:47.409
so we should

00:15:47.409 --> 00:15:49.129
accept love without understanding.

00:15:49.370 --> 00:15:49.730
But this

00:15:49.730 --> 00:15:50.649
doesn't seem right.

00:15:51.200 --> 00:15:52.169
This blanket disposal

00:15:52.169 --> 00:15:53.730
of understanding ignores

00:15:53.730 --> 00:15:54.669
how some people

00:15:54.669 --> 00:15:55.590
are prone to

00:15:55.590 --> 00:15:56.440
be more misunderstood

00:15:56.529 --> 00:15:57.370
than others due

00:15:57.370 --> 00:15:59.450
to socio-historical inequalities.

00:15:59.700 --> 00:16:00.070
When a woman

00:16:00.070 --> 00:16:01.070
is cognizant of

00:16:01.070 --> 00:16:01.929
the unequal social

00:16:02.220 --> 00:16:03.129
position between her

00:16:03.129 --> 00:16:03.669
and her male

00:16:03.669 --> 00:16:04.460
partner, for example,

00:16:05.230 --> 00:16:05.850
she feels more

00:16:05.850 --> 00:16:07.190
vulnerable to domination

00:16:07.549 --> 00:16:08.159
instead of partnership.

00:16:08.350 --> 00:16:09.169
Too many guys

00:16:09.169 --> 00:16:10.269
think they're a concept,

00:16:10.350 --> 00:16:11.809
or I complete them,

00:16:12.149 --> 00:16:12.649
or

00:16:12.850 --> 00:16:13.909
I'm gonna
make them alive.

00:16:14.299 --> 00:16:15.570
Being understood might matter

00:16:15.570 --> 00:16:16.210
more to the woman,

00:16:16.659 --> 00:16:17.850
because women's experiences

00:16:17.899 --> 00:16:18.730
are prone to

00:16:18.759 --> 00:16:19.500
systemic misunderstanding.

00:16:20.320 --> 00:16:20.950
Many women grew

00:16:20.950 --> 00:16:22.289
up in patriarchal families

00:16:22.409 --> 00:16:23.169
where their needs were

00:16:23.169 --> 00:16:24.110
often misunderstood.

00:16:24.139 --> 00:16:25.029
There is a

00:16:25.029 --> 00:16:26.190
disproportionate number of

00:16:26.360 --> 00:16:27.049
cases of women

00:16:27.049 --> 00:16:27.929
being dismissed by

00:16:27.929 --> 00:16:30.129
doctors for overreacting about

00:16:30.129 --> 00:16:31.409
their symptoms or not

00:16:31.409 --> 00:16:32.929
understanding their own bodies,

00:16:33.200 --> 00:16:33.789
only to later

00:16:33.789 --> 00:16:35.450
discover an actual serious

00:16:35.450 --> 00:16:36.909
medical issue. Thus,

00:16:37.220 --> 00:16:38.350
being understood can help

00:16:38.350 --> 00:16:40.070
reassure that these unjust

00:16:40.070 --> 00:16:41.350
patterns will not seep

00:16:41.399 --> 00:16:42.580
into her personal relationship.

00:16:43.070 --> 00:16:43.750
Moreover, we

00:16:43.750 --> 00:16:44.539
might also ask,

00:16:44.850 --> 00:16:45.350
who has the

00:16:45.440 --> 00:16:46.450
privilege of being loved

00:16:46.450 --> 00:16:47.309
without being understood?

00:16:47.690 --> 00:16:48.730
For some, an

00:16:48.730 --> 00:16:50.169
intimate relationship is the

00:16:50.169 --> 00:16:51.289
only safe space to

00:16:51.620 --> 00:16:52.720
experience their true self.

00:16:53.029 --> 00:16:53.789
The second option

00:16:53.789 --> 00:16:54.210
for how to

00:16:54.210 --> 00:16:54.809
move forward then,

00:16:55.090 --> 00:16:55.929
and the option I

00:16:56.000 --> 00:16:56.889
tentatively endorse,

00:16:57.320 --> 00:16:58.129
is to change what

00:16:58.129 --> 00:16:58.990
we expect out

00:16:58.990 --> 00:17:00.529
of understanding in love.

00:17:00.820 --> 00:17:01.610
Being understood in

00:17:01.610 --> 00:17:02.750
love is not purely

00:17:02.750 --> 00:17:03.990
an intellectual activity.

00:17:04.400 --> 00:17:04.970
It's not enough

00:17:04.970 --> 00:17:06.349
to remember facts like

00:17:06.349 --> 00:17:07.109
their favorite

00:17:07.200 --> 00:17:08.190
restaurant or artist,

00:17:08.650 --> 00:17:09.410
or even deeper

00:17:09.410 --> 00:17:11.049
information like their trauma.

00:17:11.380 --> 00:17:12.430
Because humans are

00:17:12.430 --> 00:17:13.299
not stable objects,

00:17:13.829 --> 00:17:14.549
and we don't relate

00:17:14.549 --> 00:17:15.130
to our own

00:17:15.319 --> 00:17:16.109
facts in the same

00:17:16.109 --> 00:17:17.019
way at all times.

00:17:17.509 --> 00:17:18.569
We are subjects who

00:17:18.569 --> 00:17:19.470
can and should

00:17:19.470 --> 00:17:20.369
be allowed to change.

00:17:20.769 --> 00:17:21.269
That doesn't mean

00:17:21.269 --> 00:17:22.349
we should expect nothing

00:17:22.400 --> 00:17:23.109
from our lovers.

00:17:23.410 --> 00:17:24.049
Of course,

00:17:24.200 --> 00:17:25.250
love also requires

00:17:25.869 --> 00:17:26.829
responsibility and commitment.

00:17:27.089 --> 00:17:27.750
But perhaps the

00:17:27.829 --> 00:17:28.569
kind of understanding

00:17:28.940 --> 00:17:30.250
required for love includes

00:17:30.250 --> 00:17:31.690
being okay with not

00:17:31.690 --> 00:17:32.450
understanding sometimes.

00:17:33.440 --> 00:17:33.970
Going back to

00:17:33.970 --> 00:17:34.569
what I said about

00:17:34.569 --> 00:17:35.450
Iris Murdoch earlier,

00:17:35.690 --> 00:17:36.549
one of the ways

00:17:36.549 --> 00:17:37.289
in which knowing

00:17:37.289 --> 00:17:38.529
and understanding might be

00:17:38.660 --> 00:17:40.390
different is that understanding

00:17:40.390 --> 00:17:41.170
is like a

00:17:41.170 --> 00:17:42.509
"just and loving" vision

00:17:42.849 --> 00:17:43.569
that makes you feel

00:17:43.569 --> 00:17:44.970
seen even if it

00:17:44.970 --> 00:17:47.160
clashes with "objective" facts.

00:17:47.720 --> 00:17:48.230
Think about that

00:17:48.230 --> 00:17:49.430
feeling of reuniting with

00:17:49.430 --> 00:17:50.549
someone you loved after

00:17:50.549 --> 00:17:51.950
being separated for years,

00:17:52.200 --> 00:17:53.089
and still getting

00:17:53.089 --> 00:17:53.789
them as if

00:17:53.789 --> 00:17:54.559
they'd never left.

00:17:54.920 --> 00:17:55.730
These estranged

00:17:55.730 --> 00:17:56.670
lovers don't know

00:17:56.670 --> 00:17:57.549
many facts about

00:17:57.549 --> 00:17:58.180
each other anymore.

00:17:58.720 --> 00:17:59.309
Maybe they listen

00:17:59.309 --> 00:18:00.299
to different music now.

00:18:00.759 --> 00:18:01.690
Maybe they hold different

00:18:01.690 --> 00:18:02.619
spiritual beliefs.

00:18:02.970 --> 00:18:03.569
But those aren't

00:18:03.569 --> 00:18:04.789
necessary for seeing

00:18:04.789 --> 00:18:05.750
the other as a

00:18:06.089 --> 00:18:06.599
particular subject.

00:18:07.309 --> 00:18:08.170
Understanding has to

00:18:08.170 --> 00:18:09.130
be flexible so that

00:18:09.130 --> 00:18:09.940
when love changes,

00:18:10.329 --> 00:18:10.970
you don't feel your

00:18:10.970 --> 00:18:11.630
sense of self

00:18:11.630 --> 00:18:13.099
being attacked or neglected.

00:18:13.569 --> 00:18:14.109
To be loved

00:18:14.109 --> 00:18:15.029
is to be understood.

00:18:15.529 --> 00:18:16.369
And to be understood

00:18:16.369 --> 00:18:17.819
is to SEE me,

00:18:18.279 --> 00:18:18.890
even when you

00:18:18.890 --> 00:18:20.390
struggle to recognize me.

00:18:22.779 --> 00:18:23.759
With a topic like this,

00:18:23.880 --> 00:18:24.740
there is always

00:18:24.740 --> 00:18:25.480
more that I wish

00:18:25.480 --> 00:18:26.079
I could say,

00:18:26.220 --> 00:18:27.019
or things I wish

00:18:27.019 --> 00:18:28.160
I could clarify better.

00:18:28.380 --> 00:18:28.880
But I guess

00:18:28.880 --> 00:18:29.680
that's your task

00:18:29.779 --> 00:18:30.339
to help me out

00:18:30.339 --> 00:18:30.940
in the comments.

00:18:31.299 --> 00:18:31.819
What does being

00:18:31.819 --> 00:18:33.039
understood or being loved

00:18:33.039 --> 00:18:33.680
mean to you?

00:18:33.680 --> 00:18:34.700
I also want

00:18:34.700 --> 00:18:35.900
to shamelessly plug my

00:18:35.900 --> 00:18:37.059
Patreon where I upload

00:18:37.059 --> 00:18:38.099
exclusive videos.

00:18:38.099 --> 00:18:39.680
I explain cool philosophy

00:18:39.680 --> 00:18:41.099
papers and book chapters.

00:18:41.420 --> 00:18:42.420
Recently, I did Raymond

00:18:42.420 --> 00:18:44.140
Guise's chapter on ideology.

00:18:44.480 --> 00:18:44.859
What the

00:18:44.859 --> 00:18:45.799
heck is ideology?

00:18:46.319 --> 00:18:47.079
In our Brain

00:18:47.079 --> 00:18:48.859
Nourishment series episode 6,

00:18:49.220 --> 00:18:49.839
we got Raymond

00:18:49.839 --> 00:18:50.839
Geuss's book chapter,

00:18:51.000 --> 00:18:52.119
Ideology. And also

00:18:52.119 --> 00:18:53.440
Susan Sontag's essay,

00:18:53.579 --> 00:18:54.420
The Artist as the

00:18:54.640 --> 00:18:55.140
Exemplary Sufferer.

00:18:55.779 --> 00:18:56.299
There was no

00:18:56.299 --> 00:18:58.700
metaphysical or aesthetic inevitability

00:18:58.700 --> 00:18:59.440
about his death.

00:18:59.779 --> 00:19:00.819
But something spurred

00:19:00.819 --> 00:19:01.940
a desperation in the

00:19:02.079 --> 00:19:02.740
public to make

00:19:02.740 --> 00:19:03.859
David's suffering and

00:19:03.859 --> 00:19:05.279
eventual suicide cohere

00:19:05.279 --> 00:19:06.059
with his artistry.

00:19:06.420 --> 00:19:06.759
If you want

00:19:06.759 --> 00:19:07.619
to support my channel,

00:19:07.779 --> 00:19:08.779
you can consider subbing

00:19:08.779 --> 00:19:10.019
to my Patreon, perhaps.

00:19:10.599 --> 00:19:11.380
It's hard work

00:19:11.420 --> 00:19:12.220
to make these videos

00:19:12.220 --> 00:19:13.180
and I really

00:19:13.180 --> 00:19:13.640
want to be

00:19:13.640 --> 00:19:14.420
able to be more

00:19:14.420 --> 00:19:15.819
active in 2026,

00:19:16.180 --> 00:19:17.240
even as I'm

00:19:17.240 --> 00:19:18.240
dredging through law school.

00:19:18.240 --> 00:19:19.339
Thank you so much

00:19:19.339 --> 00:19:19.839
for watching,

00:19:20.259 --> 00:19:21.339
let's keep talking, and

00:19:21.339 --> 00:19:22.019
I hope to

00:19:22.019 --> 00:19:22.799
hear from you soon.

